Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要砍掉…『七鄉』！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是元老院的一致意見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』的開花給世界帶來了多大危機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在危機已經變成現實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不可固守不出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 這個城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著『七鄉』的毀滅而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一個城鎮的代價便可以拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個…城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個城鎮毀滅了 妖怪們會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從円神出現開始 妳以為過了多長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間沒有做出成果的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的撤離就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是作為町長最後的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:36.85,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(475,325)}荊棘之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前花剛剛開 這次又是這種奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會又是你們做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 町長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是明擺著的嗎 沒關…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關…系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 元老院準備想要切斷『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌亂的衝進去又會被土地神幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界已經被破壞的現在 不是還有辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說過了的 其他的妖怪優先治療
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 『調率』是非常危險的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍錯一點 秋名會和送歸的妖怪一起到那個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了就好 今後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被『調率』的妖怪會非常痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 並不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 『調率』是修正人界和妖界的次元偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妖怪更加方便進入那邊的世界而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比被滅殺要輕鬆很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為那就如字面意思是殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華 妳沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 樹裡幫我戴上的新枷似乎很奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡邏中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不會猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長好長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很長 但是很暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要安靜一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 已經可以說話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕…留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上這個就看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍微有點長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 所以才說的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿給我 幫妳修短
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身行李是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正準備去避難…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好在城外有棲身的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避難？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從生活相談事務所的人那聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「為了以防萬一 請準備好」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 空地或者體育館都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 對不起 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託過了 但是果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 說到收容妖怪 什麼地方的城鎮都會討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會有這城鎮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒時間消沉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無處可去的居民還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得下了避難的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是存在可能性 為了萬一的時候做準備而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是町長不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長怎麼能不優先考慮居民的安全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只是為了萬一 秋名也這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼 抱歉 樹裡那裡人手不夠 去幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄城鎮而逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有說這種事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽從元老院的擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把居民從城鎮撤離出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元老院會立刻砍掉『七鄉』的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道要為了不砍掉而留下居民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在這樣做會給居民帶來多餘的不安而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上存在危險的可能 怎麼會是無用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要逃避而已不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從円神身邊逃避不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道城鎮安全了 就馬上會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神嗎 已經刻不容緩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始切斷『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回小姐那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『八彩』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在騷亂之中已經被對方得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從外部送入妖力 已經完全把『七鄉』吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方動了腦筋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力這東西的話 將其增輻也能從遠處進行傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和電波一個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨她去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬她一個人沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這點程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『火焰噴射器』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物由我們來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 把姬帶到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？故障？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用…我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『圍』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終段『大花火』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…由我親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又被大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快送到樹裡小姐那去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還說再開心一會的 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下已成定局了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神不是無法離開自己負責的土地的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然從那麼遠的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳已經放棄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是龍的化身 傷勢並沒有那麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過所積累疲勞也並不尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站到現在也只能用不可思議來形容了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她一直都在練功…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 生命倒無危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時休息下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來後一定是這種表情就跑外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別阻止她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我必須去看看其他患者了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部自己來背負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元老院沒察覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力將力量限制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要砍也砍不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 城鎮裡離『七鄉』最遠的地方是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心部 元老院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 請到元老院避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是管理城鎮的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間說明了 這裡很危險 大家快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是櫻真町『七鄉』即將開花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即去元老院避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請避難 『七鄉』的開花是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華妳不用來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是全部人員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面還有一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要叫她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去找姬定會碰釘子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹裡小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定在等你哦 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒忘過這天花板了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從這傷之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實什麼都沒改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣也是想努力下的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡全力練習 公務 巡邏 都是一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍槍也用不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有什麼情況 也都是讓秋名你們出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為町長 為人所愛 為城鎮所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍所愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為町長 作為町長卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀的事 我也不想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡銀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我必須要保護城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為町長本不應該說這些的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最差勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡給大家帶來痛苦 自己卻什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該如何是好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起保護城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥說過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與秋名 與姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來保護城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不靜養是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼艱巨的任務 不會那麼快就結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 但現在就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要姬的力量的時候一定會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 能幫我按摩下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 客人身體好僵哦 凝固的8 BEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當神也有很多煩心事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好想瞭解下神仙大人哦 講來聽聽吧 講來聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 下回是我的「不准出手事」的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 煩躁死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著按下腰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神也會積累呢 贅肉
